.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f72a5a918f00dbe164ea7fd693fe40365dd66d8d","tid":1662063,"uid":79746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"37aeb541573266109e720151da0c80841e187dc5","tid":1662063,"uid":231583,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T14:04:22.000Z","msg":"入去遊行嗌口號靜坐之類有無得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等佢唔洗做生意"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T04:24:35.000Z","msg":"做唔做都係連登吹左風先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdbabfa3230434e3508e85d8fc4a834999ac02f2","tid":1662063,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ab8998d561bd824f28eaa2b4ddffa94e931b258","tid":1662063,"uid":17646,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T13:58:44.000Z","msg":"整番個TG放題X工展會先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T04:25:09.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n［第十期牆紙］訴求在沉默中進化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1662489/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1662489/page/1</a><br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=hAhx4mZ6jCiP%2Fv5W8BSz9sorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=b7b64b4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\n歡迎投稿 : <a href=\"https://padlet.com/lennonnewshk/6g5yp3tllkxx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpadlet.com%2Flennonnewshk%2F6g5yp3tllkxx&d=hAhx4mZ6jCiP%2Fv5W8BSz9sorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=3b01694e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://padlet.com/lennonnewshk/6g5yp3tllkxx</a>"},{"pid":"347085edab3828b2841417bc9e300a680e219966","tid":1662063,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T04:25:13.000Z","msg":"工展會搵鬼去<br />\n野又比出面貴<br />\n食物又貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fu